50|$|Yasmin Akhter was a 14 {{year old}} {{domestic}} help in Dhaka. She {{was returning to}} her hometown in Dashmile area in Dinajpur on 24 August 1995. She was offered a lift by members of Bangladesh <b>police</b> <b>in</b> a <b>police</b> <b>van.</b> She was then raped and killed by three members of Bangladesh Police.|$|R
