50|$|In Tennessee, a {{prisoner}} Colin Evans (Idris Elba) is <b>in</b> a <b>police</b> <b>van</b> {{on the way}} to court with two policemen. It is revealed that Colin has been in prison for over 5 years for manslaughter. He pleas to the court to be granted parole, saying that he is a changed person. The court denies parole, claiming that he is not trustworthy enough. On the way back to prison, a frustrated Colin deceives the policemen in the car and murders both mercilessly, and escapes with the van.|$|R
